<p>
The focus is on practical usage — how to actually use these tools to save time, improve output quality, and manage digital work more effectively without spending money.
</p>

<h3>4. Tracking Your Growth & Earnings</h3>
<p>
Growth without tracking is just guesswork. This section teaches students how to monitor their progress using simple metrics and tools.
</p>

<p>
Learners understand how to measure performance, identify what’s working, and make data-driven decisions. This helps them improve consistently rather than repeating ineffective strategies.
</p>

<h3>5. Building Your Team & Network</h3>
